DNR the company is not proposing to increase their issued and Outstanding Shares OS they want to increase their Authorized Shares AS Some here do not know what the difference is and think the proposed increase in Authorized Shares is immediate dilution which it is not A company can have a Billion Authorized Shares but only 500000 issued and Outstanding Shares It is not dilution unless in the future some of the Authorized Shares are offered or converted into issued and Outstanding Shares for any number of reasons They can be used for future acquisition purposes or public offerings to raise revenues Some companies even increase their Authorized Shares to lessen the chance of a hostile takeover
